</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I wouldn&apos;t, although the book isn&apos;t quite graphic per say and the book focuses more on the dogs after they escape, the book does feature animal testin<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">â€¦more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I wouldn't, although the book isn't quite graphic per say and the book focuses more on the dogs after they escape, the book does feature animal testing for a good part of the beginning (with some animal deaths), along with some scenes throughout the book of farmer's trying to hunt the dogs. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

<div class='flagAnswer'>
<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link1124483" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=1124483&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1245606-i-m-very-sensitive-to-animal-abuse-and-it%2Fanswers%2F1124483-i-wouldn-t-although">flag</a>
</div>
<ul class='communityQAFooter answerFooter'>
</ul>

</div>
