      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/826957-the-plague-dogs">Quotes from The Plague Dogs</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Dangerous thing, a name. Someone might catch hold of you by it, mightn't they?&rdquo;</span>
